text: The service was stone cold. Walked into the shop the uncle play his guitar but never even service me as the customer. Will not go in again. This type of service i very worried after buying. No thanks ya.
Shop keeper is awesome! He tested out the guitar and played various songs before purchase! Awesome service!

Just bought one of the MTG Strats here. Plays great for a budget guitar (actually just plays great!). Pleasant hour in the shop ..friendly service and tried out the Luthier 'own brand' acoustic .. Which seemed like a lot of guitar for not much money. Would reccommend the shop and product.

By the way the guitat I couldnt remember the name of Westone ( Matsumoko )  ..its a Pantera X350MA. Dan
